Package com.snc.ds.stats.stl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CyclicSubSeriesSmoother
    Encapsulate the complexity of smoothing the cyclic sub-series in a separate class.
    CyclicSubSeriesSmoother.Builder
    Use Builder to simplify complex construction patterns.
    LoessSettings
    LoessSettings - immutable settings class for specifying the triple of width/jump/degree used to initialize the LOESS interpolators.
    LoessSmoother
    LoessSmoother uses LOESS interpolation to compute a smoothed data set from a regularly-spaced set of input data.
    LoessSmoother.Builder  
    SeasonalTrendLoess
    Java implementation of the Seasonal-Trend-Loess algorithm for evenly spaced data.
    SeasonalTrendLoess.Builder
    Builder class for SeasonalTrendLoess decomposition
    SeasonalTrendLoess.Decomposition  
    StlFitStats
    StlFitStats analyzes an STL decomposition, computing basic statistics for the original data and the decomposition.
